                        "string": "A dependency on another module, identified by its name and (optionally) the package which provides it. When the package is omitted, the resolver searches all packages in scope; a duplicate module name across packages is a resolution error which can be disambiguated by naming the intended package explicitly."}}}]}}}}}},
